{"tid":1777216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《華爾街日報》：美國會欲在國防法案中禁止採購中國巴士和軌道車","createTime":"2019-12-10T05:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T08:03:06.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99c3a4591bd9fde48b42e2f5bc9535734096ba81","tid":1777216,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"中美貿易談判前景未明之際，繼有報道指中國指示公家機關必須在3年內移除國外品牌的電腦設備及軟體，據報美國國會希望禁止使用政府資金，購買部分中國產品。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息指，美國國會參眾兩院已達成共識，在必定要通過的國防政策法案中，加入禁止使用聯邦政府資金購買中國巴士及鐵路車輛，但稱禁令不包括現有合同。另外，亦準備禁止美國軍方購買中國製無人機。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，相關法案將影響一直大舉進軍美國鐵路車輛市場的中車 （01766） ，以及通過旗下向美國銷售電動巴士的比亞迪 （01211） 。其中，估計中車年銷售額為180億美元。至於禁買中國無人機，料對DJI（大疆創新）帶來挑戰。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2516581/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2516581%2F&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=02f70db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2516581/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/congress-wants-to-ban-chinese-buses-railcars-in-defense-bill-11575927925?mod=hp_lead_pos6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fcongress-wants-to-ban-chinese-buses-railcars-in-defense-bill-11575927925%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos6&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cbHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=5c71a1d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/congress-wants-to-ban-chinese-buses-railcars-in-defense-bill-11575927925?mod=hp_lead_pos6</a>"},{"pid":"08ec8fd5f4b5ebdce17b1b3cc5711da0e55d8873","tid":1777216,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"c